## 11. Document Maintenance

This document is a living spec. When requirements change:
- Update the relevant section
- Add an entry to the changelog below
- If the change affects the schema, update `SCHEMA.md` first

When the agent makes an implementation decision not covered here, it records it in `DECISIONS.md`, not in this file.

